{"title":"2020-10-27 白山","virttualPath":null,"html":"<div class=\"markdown-body\"><h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-2020-10-27-白山\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#2020-10-27-%E7%99%BD%E5%B1%B1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>2020-10-27 白山</h1>\n<p>平日休みで白山へ。登りはじめの気温 (標高1200m) は 1 度前後。移動距離は 17km, 獲得標高は 1700m</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-063659-IMG_20201027_063658.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-063659-IMG_20201027_063658.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"朝の紅葉\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>こういうヘリが荷運びをしてるんだけど、人が搭乗する場所ってあるか？まさかドローン？</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-070029-IMG_20201027_070026.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-070029-IMG_20201027_070026.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"薄型ヘリ\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p><em>追記</em> その後調べてみると <a href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%82%AB%E3%83%9E%E3%83%B3_K-MAX\" rel=\"nofollow\">カマン K-MAX</a> という機種らしい。ドローンで荷運びが全部できるようになれば、通常業務での人的損耗リスクはなくなるわけだけど、まだまだ先だろうねぇ。</p>\n<p>南竜はどうやら au の電波は掴んでいたようだ。Docomo は確認してない。</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-082829-Screenshot_20201027_082829.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-082829-Screenshot_20201027_082829.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"南竜\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>新しく増やした方がジムになってた。今日は行く時間がないので、また来年…</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-094955-Screenshot_20201027-094955.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-094955-Screenshot_20201027-094955.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"アルプス展望台\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>山頂めぐり。雪の中をずぼずぼ歩く。</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-120335-P_20201027_120335.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-120335-P_20201027_120335.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"大汝山頂\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-121037-P_20201027_121037.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-121037-P_20201027_121037.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"大汝山頂社\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-125948-ricoh360.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-125948-ricoh360.jpg\" alt=\"myimage://2020/2020-10-27/20201027-125948-ricoh360.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-132424-P_20201027_132424.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-132424-P_20201027_132424.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"御前峰 山頂\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-132538-P_20201027_132538.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-132538-P_20201027_132538.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"白山 山頂社\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>室堂周辺の雪だけ融けてる。</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-134821-P_20201027_134821.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-134821-P_20201027_134821.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"室堂\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>あとはひたすら下山、下山</p>\n<p>予定通り紅葉は美しい。 <strong>どの山域でも紅葉は美しい。</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-155429-P_20201027_155429.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-155429-P_20201027_155429.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"登山道の紅葉1\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-155715-P_20201027_155715.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-155715-P_20201027_155715.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"登山道の紅葉2\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-154942-P_20201027_154942.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-154942-P_20201027_154942.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"登山道の紅葉3\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-155153-P_20201027_155153.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-155153-P_20201027_155153.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"登山道の紅葉4\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-155415-ricoh360.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-155415-ricoh360.jpg\" alt=\"myimage://2020/2020-10-27/20201027-155415-ricoh360.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-155614-ricoh360.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-155614-ricoh360.jpg\" alt=\"myimage://2020/2020-10-27/20201027-155614-ricoh360.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>朝みる紅葉と夕陽に当たった紅葉は全然違う。</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-160717-P_20201027_160717.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-160717-P_20201027_160717.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"別当出合の紅葉\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-165115-IMG_20201027_165114.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-165115-IMG_20201027_165114.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"別当出合の紅葉2\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"2020-10-27/20201027-165746-P_20201027_165746.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-10-27/20201027-165746-P_20201027_165746.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"市ノ瀬までの道\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n</div>","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"随筆","updated":"2020-12-07T08:49:00","published":"2020-10-27T20:27:50"}